# Checkins

* TOC
{:toc}

## Object

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
`id` | `string` | unique identifier
`store` | `int` | store id **expandable**
`reward` | `number` | How many bitcons were rewarded for checking in.


## Create

    POST /checkins

### Input

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
`qrcode` | `string` | **Required** value received from scanning the QR code.
`coords` | `hash` | **Required** Coordinates of the hunter when they scanned the QR code.
`coords[lat]` | `number` | **Required**
`coords[long]` | `number` | **Required**


## Retrieve

    GET /checkins/:id


## List

A list of the current hunter's checkins.

    GET /checkins


